        "synopsis": {
            "value": "Through fate mailman Dong-baek Ku (Hwang Jung-Min) and famous actress Ji-su Han (Kim Ah-Joong) crosses paths and eventually become involved in a contract marriage.\n\nIt all starts when actress Ji-su gets involved in a car crash with her secret boyfriend driving the car. Desperate to cover up their relationship, Ji-su drags an innocent bystander, mailman Dong-baek Gu into the car, while her boyfriend flees the scene. The paparazzi then arrives and takes their photos. This brings Dong-baek Gu instant notoriety and things turn more bizarre when he continues to act as Ji-su's boyfriend.",
